      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>VPN/ExpressRoute<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>—Communicates and replicates data between on-premises servers and Azure over a VPN connection.",
      "pos": [
        6653,
        6767
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You'll need to set up a site-to-site VPN or an <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>ExpressRoute<ept id=\"p1\">](../expressroute-introduction.md)</ept> connection between the on-premises site and your Azure network.",
