        52496,
        52563
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        52571,
        52754
      ],
      "content": "Install the latest updates for the process server as described in <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Step 5: Install latest updates<ept id=\"p1\">](#step-5-install-latest-updates)</ept>, and make sure that the process server is available."
    },
    {
      "content": "Ensure there's network connectivity between the source machine and the process server, and that the source machine is accessible from the process server.",
      "pos": [
        52759,
        52912
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Configure the Windows firewall to allow <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>File and Printer Sharing<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> and <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Windows Management Instrumentation<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        52918,
        53030
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Under Windows Firewall settings, select the option “Allow an app or feature through Firewall” and select the applications as shown in the picture below.",
      "pos": [
        53031,
        53183
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For machines that belong to a domain you can configure the firewall policy with a Group Policy Object.",
      "pos": [
        53184,
        53286
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Firewall settings",
      "pos": [
        53294,
        53311
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The account used to perform the push installation must be in the Administrators group on the machine you want to protect.",
